title: Charch on #92Noon
description:
PA is off, Paul Charchian is in. It's the summer sports abyss and Charch dives head first into the awfulness of grad parties. His tumultuous love affair with vinyl, and how they found their way back to each other.
The swarm of technology invading our cars. And Resident Twins expert, Aaron Gleeman, stops by for some Twins talk.
